Package: loco
Title: Local Correlation Tracking of Time Series (LoCo)
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Adam", "Shen", , "adamshen1@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implementation of the local correlation (LoCo) similarity
    score for time series, proposed by Papadimitriou, S., Sun, J., and Yu,
    P.S., in the paper "Local Correlation Tracking in Time Series"
    <doi:10.1109/ICDM.2006.99>.
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: https://adamoshen.github.io/loco, https://github.com/adamoshen/loco
